frames.caption: A surreal scene features a large, intricately detailed figure with a top hat, composed of swirling colors and textures. The figure's profile is set against a backdrop of towering crystalline structures, with a small human figure standing on one of the peaks, gazing at the giant visage. The atmosphere is otherworldly, with vibrant purples and blues creating a mystical ambiance.

A lone human figure stands on a peak, adding a sense of scale and wonder.
